  "description": "Simple diagram showcasing the mqtt pub/sub nodes w/ a CEL condition node.\n \n1. Sub node subscribes to the \"order/v1\" topic with a timeout of 5s and waits for a state == IDLE condition.\n2. If Ok, terminates the workflow else, goes through the Err branch.\n3. If Err output is Timeout, retry the subscriber node and publish \"state\":\"IDLE\" to \"order/v1\".\n\nThe workflow will timeout once -> go through the error branch and retry -> go through the Ok branch -> Terminate workflow  ",
